-- Eni Plans to Sell as Many as 3 Billion Euros of Bonds Over 12 Months
-- Dan Liefgreen
-- 2010-04-23T11:07:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-23/eni-s-board-approves-sale-of-as-much-as-4-billion-of-bonds-over-12-months.html

          
          
             Eni SpA said its board approved the
sale of as much as 3 billion euros of bonds over the next 12
months in one or more installments. The bonds will enable the
company to “achieve a better balance between its short-term and
long-term debt,” according to a statement.  
          
          


  


        